Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:37.85,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:41.01,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Tou~ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:51.33,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I am away from Academy City, spending time at the beach with Index.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.33,0:00:54.03,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, this wasn't voluntary on my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.41,0:00:56.45,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of this city right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:01:00.04,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the higher-ups are getting cranky about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:04.12,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate... Kamijo-chan,\Nyou'll be in a dangerous situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:06.45,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,so until the dust settles...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.45,0:01:08.96,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,...is what a couple of higher-ups are thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:13.20,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and the place you'll be going to is... let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:14.84,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:16.97,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:18.43,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:20.68,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going with you, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:23.39,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,This will be the first time I go to the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.65,0:01:25.86,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,"No" means no!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.86,0:01:30.67,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you're an illegal alien who doesn't even have a valid ID!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.67,0:01:34.40,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you try to tag along,\NI bet you'll get stopped at the city limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.35,0:01:40.07,index,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.48,0:01:46.23,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,How in the world did he just let us go without a second look?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:49.96,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...but yeah, just like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:52.50,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,we ended up here for some odd reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:58.63,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And I just get a bad feeling from the name of the place they chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:58.63,Note,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Note: "Oowarai" means big laugh/joke/jeer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:00.15,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Tou~ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:04.77,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I found a cute hat, and I'm going to give it to you as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:07.36,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:08.44,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:10.98,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Owww!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:45.15,index,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a misfortune you experienced so soon after your arrival...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:48.97,index,woman,0000,0000,0000,,This year's jellyfish season came quite early though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:52.43,index,woman,0000,0000,0000,,And thanks to that, we have no guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:54.11,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:58.28,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,It was really the first time I've seen a jellyfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.48,index,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:01.58,index,woman,0000,0000,0000,,I will come back to retrieve the first-aid kit later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:03.17,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, th-thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:04.91,index,man,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:11.33,index,man,0000,0000,0000,,We just got a call from your party-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:14.78,index,man,0000,0000,0000,,-that they'd be arriving late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.89,index,man,0000,0000,0000,,That they'll arrive tomorrow morning-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:20.45,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought we were going to see them soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:21.69,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma's-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:21.69,index alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:22.98,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:24.55,index,man,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:26.12,index,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.84,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so disappointed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:36.58,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was supposed to meet them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:43.21,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijo Touya and Kamijo Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.28,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,My parents, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:47.34,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:51.80,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.99,0:05:00.48,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Since I don't see them that often, Komoe-sensei seems to be taking care of me more than normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:02.73,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And it seems a cousin I grew up with is coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:08.26,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:09.22,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:11.65,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of people are your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:13.64,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What kind? Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:18.20,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really looking forward to seeing your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:22.63,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Touma, are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:23.74,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.52,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find out tomorrow, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:29.15,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,You're being a meanie again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:31.09,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,How much could it hurt to tell me now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:35.79,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,And you're always, always so cold, so cruel, so blunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:38.07,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,so rude, so brusque, so indifferent,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:41.23,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,so unregretful, so hard to grasp-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:41.84,index alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll find out tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:48.44,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my memories, so I obviously don't remember how my parents are,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:54.74,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,what kind of people they were, or what kind of son I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:57.24,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be able to act naturally before them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:03.79,index,Shiz,0000,0000,0000,,The red-hot Hitotsui Hajime-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:06.46,index,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:14.33,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,As such, I'm uncharacteristically nervous right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:18.68,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Heck, will they find out I lost my memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:22.93,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's no point worrying about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:26.19,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The fun will start tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:38.28,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:41.88,index,man,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:44.38,index,man,0000,0000,0000,,Your party just called now-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:47.56,index,man,0000,0000,0000,,-that they will arrive soon-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:49.63,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:27.83,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:34.76,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,You look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:35.92,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Anything different?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:38.45,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:41.67,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I wanted to hand you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:44.54,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,I went to India on my last business trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:48.64,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,This is a souvenir, a local deity called something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.11,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:54.31,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:56.84,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if you're meeting me for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.43,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, ah-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:00.18,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, let me get your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:02.46,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Take Mom's and Otohime-chan's, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.70,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:04.91,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:12.25,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This person is my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.57,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about our arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:17.25,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,We were supposed to get here last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:20.96,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,You know, we just moved,\Nso we don't know where things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:21.98,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Move?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:23.05,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.05,0:08:24.81,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,We went over this on the phone last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:25.97,index alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:28.99,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:31.94,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ever be able to see the home I was born in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:33.70,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:35.90,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Onii~chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:37.40,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:39.28,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Onii~chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:42.24,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's my cousin-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:44.69,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Onii~chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:48.12,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Onii~chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:55.17,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, Oniichan! I wanted to see you so badly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:57.90,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Touma-oniichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:00.01,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to the sea later! The sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:02.47,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:04.80,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Just hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:06.54,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,What, Oniichan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:07.82,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Not "what"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:09.34,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:11.94,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And what's with your disgusting sister acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:14.27,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,What~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:15.42,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:17.69,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring someone like her here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.69,0:09:19.40,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Heck, since when did you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:21.12,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "someone like"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:22.42,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "since when did I know her"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.61,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,She's your cousin, Otohime-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:29.70,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No, yo, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:30.34,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:30.94,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,My back-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:32.12,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,They're touching my back-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:33.92,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:39.50,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,Touma-san, is being hugged by Otohime-chan embarrassing because you haven't experienced it in some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:42.75,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you think you're doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:44.00,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:45.73,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,Touma-san, is-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:47.90,index alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you sleeping like a pig in the room just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:51.82,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Changing your clothing and teleporting, who are you, Shirai Kuroko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:56.02,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And! What's with your obvious madam-like, señora-like way of speech?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:57.11,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your mouth, Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.10,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:10:01.19,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Talking like that to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:06.74,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,I said, what's with you talking that rudely to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:18.71,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, are you saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:22.77,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...that this girl, who looks like she'd get kicked out of a R-15 movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:24.40,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...is my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:25.80,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:29.71,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,Touma-san, are you saying your mom appears younger than her age?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:32.96,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And that this electrifying shocker of a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:34.32,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...is my cousin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:36.20,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:39.06,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,They are your mother and Otohime-chan, without a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:41.32,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you, Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:52.74,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? EVERYTHING!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:55.00,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What is this surprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:57.38,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the "You've been punked" sign?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:11:00.88,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Playing around with the tender soul of a young man like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:04.70,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of grudge do you guys have against me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:06.78,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, calm down, Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:08.39,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,See, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.87,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,The swimsuit girl drawn on this pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:11.81,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Flip it and-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:13.03,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Good-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:14.28,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:15.99,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going in the middle of our conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.99,0:11:17.77,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Oniichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:18.90,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,Touma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:20.74,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Toying with me like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:23.19,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought my dad would be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:25.20,index,!MIS.,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:27.91,index,!MIS.,0000,0000,0000,,We have been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:29.97,index,!MIS.,0000,0000,0000,,Please... come in...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:32.89,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:34.89,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:37.73,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're part of this, too, Misaka sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.52,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Since when were you hiding here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:42.36,index,!MIS.,0000,0000,0000,,...huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:45.03,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, please don't mind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:48.66,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,He's a bit emotional since we haven't seen each other in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:51.38,index,!Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for staying here at our resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:54.60,index,!Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,I will take you to your rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:00.38,index,!Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Come, come. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:05.36,index,!Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, your friend is awake now it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:14.16,index,$%@$,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, good morning, Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:16.16,index,$%@$,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go eat breakfast already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:19.64,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,AHHHHHHHHHHHHH---
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:38.76,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Onii~chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:40.81,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Onii~chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:44.90,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:49.69,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I am at the beach with a Misaka Mikoto that's wearing a school swimsuit and pretending to be a sister character.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:52.61,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, this wasn't voluntary on my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:54.07,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.05,index,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}PLACEHOLDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:57.08,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to play a part in this, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.94,index alt,$%@$,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:12:58.42,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, calm down, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.04,index,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:04.88,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,In times like these, just take a dip and cool your head, Oniichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:07.38,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come over afterwards, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:13.16,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Such misfortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:17.18,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But how long is this comedy act going to last?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:19.46,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's no longer at the level of\N"You've been punked!" anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:21.00,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Cooled your head a bit now, Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:25.27,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're worrying about, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:27.52,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I'll give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:30.44,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,It's a souvenir I got on my business trip to Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:31.57,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:32.97,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:33.49,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:35.66,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Fun, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.60,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:38.58,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:44.83,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,Touma-san, Dad's taste doesn't work on you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:46.97,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-You... that-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.33,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:50.27,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,That looks perfect on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:52.80,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,It was a great idea for me to have gotten you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:55.29,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who bought this swimsuit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:57.02,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your taste, as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:57.78,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:13:59.68,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,If you go around the world on business trips,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:02.69,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,you start to see that Japanese women need to be refined a bit-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:04.73,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to me so suddenly, Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:06.73,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I am certain now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:08.79,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...that my father is a failure of a person...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:11.07,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...that he is just a damn lolicon pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:20.71,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there she comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.29,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:24.12,index,$%@$,0000,0000,0000,,Tou~ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:28.12,index,$%@$,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:30.68,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Oniichan, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:31.84,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,Touma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:32.71,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:37.73,index,tv,0000,0000,0000,,Next in the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:40.10,index,tv,0000,0000,0000,,With the political scandal that has shaken up the White House,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:45.17,index,tv,0000,0000,0000,,the President will be holding a press conference to explain the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.14,0:14:46.46,index alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's the doc doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:48.35,index,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Komori reporting from Washington, D.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:50.64,index,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,With the suspicions surrounding the Office this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:53.28,index,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,it will be interesting to see what stance the President takes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:56.65,index,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,and what will be said-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:57.66,index alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:14:59.70,index,!Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I can't see, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:00.29,index alt,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,The President has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:02.28,index,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,She is showing a calm, nonchalant face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:05.67,index,!Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:08.42,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What is Shirai Kuroko doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:09.68,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.66,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This is way too ridiculous no matter how you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:13.84,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This is too well planned for a surprise trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:16.93,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there's no point in crossing the ocean just to do this trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:19.22,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming it's not a prank...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:21.91,index,men,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:23.10,index,men,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:26.42,index,police,0000,0000,0000,,Then, take this hill road in front of you and go straight-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:27.89,index,oldota,0000,0000,0000,,Shana-tan, moe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:29.89,index,oldho,0000,0000,0000,,This person's uber annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:31.57,index,...,0000,0000,0000,,Drop the loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:32.78,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.53,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:36.59,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Oniichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:37.81,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:39.14,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:40.99,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,This was a photo from New Year's last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:44.87,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember me now, Touma-oniichan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.45,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:49.87,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,You're really weird today, Oniichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:51.34,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:53.79,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The girl in this picture is my cousin-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:55.17,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:57.03,index,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsugami Otohime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:16:01.18,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,She can't tell that her own appearance is different in this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:05.35,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:08.85,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if everyone's inside and outside are "inside out".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:12.02,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And they don't realize it themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:13.65,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:26.33,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijo Touma knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:27.79,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,He knows from experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:29.69,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's not in my memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:34.21,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,he knows that people that show up in these crazy cosplays are usually his acquaintances.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:36.03,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And thus, in these situations,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:37.87,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,the attitude I should take is-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:39.42,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, long time no-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:40.21,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,-see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:42.80,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Question no. 1 - Are you the spellcaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:45.18,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Asking question no. 1 again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:46.97,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the spellcaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.34,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:52.52,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,It is rash to say that this young man is the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:56.86,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, glad we made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:58.37,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:02.64,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,And he actually sees me properly as Tsuchimikado Motoharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:03.45,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:07.37,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,But the fact that he can properly recognize you must mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:08.78,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, Neechin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:11.79,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see any traces of that on Kami-yan's body at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:16.04,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,We must consider him the same as us; that he was able to escape the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:19.75,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I am a magician from the English Purist Church, Necessarius,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:20.76,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:24.03,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I came here for the same reason as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:26.09,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,To determine the origin of this distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:29.31,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,However, it is unreasonable to conclude that this young man is the caster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:35.74,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,I am a magician from the Russian Orthodox Church, Annihilatus,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:36.73,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Misha Croitsef. {offical name from booklet}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:42.34,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, to be able to see a magician of Annihilatus here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:45.90,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Question no. 1 - What evidence do you have to say that this man isn't the caster?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:49.41,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Question no. 2 - If not this man, who is the caster?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.43,0:17:52.11,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I can't tell what's going on here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:54.62,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Heck, what is Tsuchimikado doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:58.16,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,This young man is not a magician, but an esper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:17:59.62,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,And his level is-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:02.71,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys just going to ignore the fact that I was almost killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:03.78,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Just gonna ignore me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:05.99,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,How disagreeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:09.03,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Your rudeness and vulgar attitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:11.01,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,It appears you haven't grown at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:14.10,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This person is my acquaintance, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:16.59,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing I played dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:20.92,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,At least tell me what's going on here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:22.65,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,How about it, Kanzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:23.77,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:26.63,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,It's best to let all concerned members know what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:28.07,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,else we cannot move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:29.58,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Concerned member?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:30.44,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:35.79,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, a certain magic spell is spreading around the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:38.25,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,The structure and formula of the magic is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:42.85,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,For convenience purposes, we are calling this magic "Angel Fall".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.30,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:47.26,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know of the Tree of Sephiroth?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:51.49,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I say it's a graph that ranks the spiritual classes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:53.89,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,...of the Supreme One, angels, and humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:57.71,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, there is no way a human can attain the rank of an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:19:00.06,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,And the other way around certainly is impossible, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:03.32,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, all classes are full.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:06.78,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,However, when an angel falls to the human class-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.78,0:19:07.70,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Time out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:09.40,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Time out for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:12.21,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Having a hard time understanding, as expected?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:16.44,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, but... angels? This is too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:20.92,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,You should've experienced, firsthand, the effects of this spell, Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:21.54,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Effects?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:24.80,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, the switching of appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:27.67,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,The emergence of this messed up world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.67,0:19:29.91,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,From the distortion caused by the fall of an angel,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:33.66,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,the "appearance" and "content" of\Nthe human world has been completely messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.66,0:19:36.52,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,And now, the musical chair game is all about first come, first served.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:39.50,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,"Appearance" will quickly take the place of "content".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:40.41,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,As a result...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:43.08,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the fact that everyone's appearance is being switched around is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:47.85,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,While we don't know by whom and\Nfor what purpose this magic was cast,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:51.22,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,the important thing is the person in the middle of this distortion...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:53.26,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,...and that is you, Kami-yan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:57.62,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,You are the number one suspect in the Angel Fall incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:20:00.15,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,You escaped the effects of the magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:02.45,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,and from the viewpoint of the magicians who are trying to stop the effects from spreading,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:04.42,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,you are one who will be targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:08.55,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, it is hard to conclude\Nthe true suspect is Kamijo Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:12.23,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,One, he does not possess any magical knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:19.06,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Two, we cannot see any trace of the "load"\Ntypically seen on espers who have used magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:23.65,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Rebuttal no. 1 - This man has not been affected by the magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:30.78,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,But hey, he's got the Imagine Breaker that can nullify any kind of illusion in this world with his right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:31.69,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:32.60,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:37.04,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado, how do you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:41.09,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Number value: 40, 9, 30, 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.54,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Sum of 86.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:48.09,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Corresponding to "O' water,\Nbecome a serpent and strike like a sword"...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.87,0:20:55.90,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:59.59,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,I acknowledge this explanation as evidence for clearing him from suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:04.41,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Young man, I apologize here for pointing\Nmy blade at you for the wrong reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:07.50,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:08.78,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you no longer have any suspicion on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:12.57,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,it is a fact that Angel Fall is centered around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:15.28,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,There is a high probability that the caster is near Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.61,0:21:19.62,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,It is hard to imagine that a single caster is responsible for a spell of this scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:23.82,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,There must be a ritual location that has a barrier or a magical seal deployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:25.61,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,We'd need to destroy the ritual location...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:27.94,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,...or defeat the caster himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:31.12,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,There are only two ways to stop an Angel Fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:32.55,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:35.47,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, Tsuchimikado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:37.44,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you on this side of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:39.51,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know about my right hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:41.04,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Tsuchimikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.14,0:21:44.73,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.73,0:21:48.23,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also a member of Necessarius.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.36,0:23:27.95,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Searching for the caster that started Angel Fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:30.20,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado and I headed for Dad's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.20,0:23:32.16,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The horrible finding we made there was...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.16,0:23:34.92,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Kamijo Touya".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:37.12,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross paths,
